WEBVTT

00:00.056 --> 00:02.268
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.293 --> 00:04.929
We've studied you
in great detail, Professor.

00:04.954 --> 00:07.002
We've drawn from that
to make a proposal

00:07.027 --> 00:09.132
that would end hostilities
between us.

00:09.157 --> 00:10.823
That's why we'll never stop
fighting you.

00:10.848 --> 00:12.237
In the harnessing
facility...

00:12.262 --> 00:13.719
I saw your spikes glow.

00:13.744 --> 00:15.092
I want the harness back.

00:15.117 --> 00:16.852
Come with me.
We'll find them.

00:16.877 --> 00:17.884
We'll find them together.

00:17.909 --> 00:19.997
Well, what if it wasn't something
physical but psychological?

00:20.022 --> 00:22.264
Just like there's no way to know
what's going on inside of me.

00:22.940 --> 00:25.199
I heard they pulled a
circuit board out of Tom's head.

00:25.423 --> 00:26.765
We don't know what it is.

00:26.790 --> 00:28.668
I'll decide
who I can trust.

